            <td colspan="2" class="titulo2" valign="top"><strong>The Power of Prose:</strong> <br>
            The Feather Pillow <br>
            By: <a href="bio.php">Horacio Quiroga</a><br>
				Translated from the Spanish into the English by <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/staff/peter_robertson/bio.php">Peter Robertson</a><br>
